lead_paragraph: Marcus Rashford scored a stoppage-time winner as Manchester United broke Hull City's resistance at the death to win 1-0 at the KCOM Stadium on Saturday and keep Jose Mourinho's winning record alive at his new club.

headline.print_headline: Substitute Rashford Breaks Hull Resolve With Late Winner
